    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the juice of<strong> half </strong>your<strong> lemon[s] </strong>to a mixing bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and whisk to combine – this is your <strong>lemon dressing</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
