    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the risotto is ready, remove it from the heat and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Tip: Your risotto should be porridge-like in consistency so if it is looking a little dry, add a splash of water</p><p>Stir most of your <strong>crab meat</strong> (save some for garnish!) and your <strong>clotted cream</strong> through the risotto – this is your <strong>saffron, crab & clotted cream risotto</strong></p>",
